<p class='talk-transcript__para'>
<data class='talk-transcript__para__time'>
 8:43
</data>
<span class='talk-transcript__para__text'>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='512000' id='t-512000'>SA: So far it's chaos, but a lot of people are doing stuff, so that's good.</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='516000' id='t-516000'>We'll see what happens.</span>
</span>
</p>
<p class='talk-transcript__para'>
<data class='talk-transcript__para__time'>
 8:49
</data>
<span class='talk-transcript__para__text'>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='518000' id='t-518000'>Narrator: The first group builds a cubicle in which the walls are screens</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='522000' id='t-522000'>for the computer and for family photos.</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='525000' id='t-525000'>In the second group's scenario, the walls are alive</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='529000' id='t-529000'>and actually give Dilbert a group hug.</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='532000' id='t-532000'>(Laughter)</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='534000' id='t-534000'>Behind the humor is the idea of making the cubicle more human.)</span>
</span>
</p>
<p class='talk-transcript__para'>
<data class='talk-transcript__para__time'>
 9:11
</data>
<span class='talk-transcript__para__text'>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='540000' id='t-540000'>David Kelley: So here's the final thing, complete with orange lighting</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='543000' id='t-543000'>that follows the sun across -- that follows the tracks of the sun -- across the sky.</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='547000' id='t-547000'>So you feel that in your cubicle.</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='551000' id='t-551000'>And my favorite feature, which is a flower in a vase</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='553000' id='t-553000'>that wilts when you leave in disappointment,</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='556000' id='t-556000'>and then when you come back, it comes up to greet you, happy to see you.</span>
