 9:31
</data>
<span class='talk-transcript__para__text'>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='560000' id='t-560000'>(SA: The storage is built right into the wall.)</span>
</span>
</p>
<p class='talk-transcript__para'>
<data class='talk-transcript__para__time'>
 9:33
</data>
<span class='talk-transcript__para__text'>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='562000' id='t-562000'>DK: You know, it has homey touches like a built-in fish tank in the walls,</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='567000' id='t-567000'>or something to be aggressive with to release tension.</span>
</span>
</p>
<p class='talk-transcript__para'>
<data class='talk-transcript__para__time'>
 9:42
</data>
<span class='talk-transcript__para__text'>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='571000' id='t-571000'>(SA: Customizable for the boss of your choice.)</span>
